      private double[][] calTimeMatrix(java.util.List<BapNode.BranchArc> historyBranchArcs)
      get new time matrix after branch, here we forbid arcs by setting their travel time to big enough:
      1 if brachValue = 0，set the travel time of branch arc to big enough;
      2 if branchValue = 1，set the travel time of the arcs starting from "fromVertex" or ending at "toVertex" to be big enough except branch arc.

      • calTimeMatrix

        private double[][] calTimeMatrix(java.util.List<BapNode.BranchArc> historyBranchArcs)
        get new time matrix after branch, here we forbid arcs by setting their travel time to big enough:
        1 if brachValue = 0，set the travel time of branch arc to big enough;
        2 if branchValue = 1，set the travel time of the arcs starting from "fromVertex" or ending at "toVertex" to be big enough except branch arc.
        参数:
        historyBranchArcs - all branch arcs of current node's ancestors in the branch and bound tree
        返回:
        new time matrix after branch
